cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.NE 

This paper proposes a method to accelerate model-free, off-policy deep RL algorithms. The paper focuses on improving the convergence and sample efficiency of RL algorithms, which are core topics in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses the application of the proposed method to control systems, which suggests the possibility of cs.SY (Systems and Control) as another potential category. Finally, the paper involves neural networks, which is a common technique in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
